---
// Solution.astro
---

<section class="solution section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center section-title">
      FreeSpeech makes the invisible rules of language visible.
    </h2>

    <div class="solution-grid">
      <div class="solution-card card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <span class="icon">🧩</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Pictures, not rules.</h3>
        <p>
          Every word is a picture. Every grammatical relationship — tense,
          number, person, sentence type — is a visual property on a grid.
          Children manipulate language the same way they'd arrange blocks: by
          seeing and touching.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="solution-card card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <span class="icon">✨</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Instant, correct sentences.</h3>
        <p>
          FreeSpeech doesn't just let children arrange pictures — it understands
          the grammar behind the arrangement. Swap "I" for "he" and watch "eat"
          become "eats" automatically. The child sees cause and effect, not a
          rule to memorize.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="solution-card card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <span class="icon">🔊</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Spoken aloud.</h3>
        <p>
          Every sentence is spoken in a clear, natural voice. The child hears
          their own thought — assembled from pictures — expressed as real
          language. That moment is powerful.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-16);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .solution-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-8);
  }

  .solution-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-12) var(--spacing-8);
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-full);
    background-color: var(--color-primary-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-6);
  }

  .icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .solution-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
  }

  .solution-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .solution-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
